{"tid":826654,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【🌋樓爆2018】大窩口開放式呎價2.2萬😨等跌八成","createTime":"2018-09-18T11:20:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-18T11:20:33.000Z","uid":43146,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c3f07bef47f1c5401b0dff0329b3bded29e01864","tid":826654,"uid":43146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T11:20:33.000Z","msg":"縉庭山開放戶呎撲2.2萬 屋苑新高 (18:23)<br />\n文章日期：2018年9月18日<br />\n<br />\n整體二手交投雖然減慢，但細單位仍受追捧，大窩口縉庭山有開放式戶，實呎做價直逼2.2萬元，創屋苑新高。土地註冊處資料顯示，上述縉庭山1座低層C室，實用219方呎，採開放式間隔，上月底以480萬元易手，實呎21918元，呎價創屋苑新高；原業主2014年5月以275萬元購入單位，持貨4年，帳面獲利205萬元或75%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantp2.php?node=1537266340267&amp;issue=20180918\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantp2.php%3Fnode%3D1537266340267%26issue%3D20180918&d=qu2zEATov2gwXhtY4ibB6P%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=6dbccb1f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantp2.php%3Fnode%3D1537266340267%26issue%3D20180918&h=9bc000c4\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantp2.php?node=1537266340267&amp;issue=20180918</a>"}]}